data.description: Welcome to Evans! 4th NON CONFORMING BEDROOM ON LOWER LEVEL, just add a closet! NO HOA neighborhood! NEW - 2 year old exterior paint. NEW - 2 year old roof! NEWER windows. NEW sliding backdoor! NEW front Door! Mature landscape. HUGE, beautiful backyard, impressive lot size. Garden area! Shed Stays! XL Garage room for extra storage, extra tall ceilings, walking into a true mud room set up. Main Floor Laundry. Cork floors. HUGE Concrete entertainment patio! Wood burning fireplace with brick surround. Double living/seating rooms! Clawfoot bathtub! Washer and Dryer included!
